# Records `ncli decode` on a npub. Run via `just vhs decode`.

Output docs/vhs/decode.gif

Set Shell "bash"
Set FontSize 15
Set Width 1200
Set Height 300
Set Padding 20
Set Theme "Dracula"
Set TypingSpeed 40ms

Type "ncli decode npub1sg6plzptd64u62a878hep2kev88swjh3tw00gjsfl8f237lmu63q0uf63m"
Sleep 500ms
Enter
Sleep 2s
